{
    "headline": "Cape Malay Pickled Fish",
    "name": "Cape Malay Pickled Fish",
    "description": "Pickled fish made with tender cod fillets covered with a sweet, spicy, and aromatic pickling liquid is a traditional and delicious Cape Town Easter meal.",
    "recipeCuisine": [
        "South African",
